Reports and Dashboards
Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards
Create standard reports on single or multiple related data model objects (DMOs) or Calculated Insights, or build a custom report type on DMO fields and records from Data Cloud. Visualize KPIs and trends from Data Cloud reports in your dashboards.

Find answers to business questions with Data Cloud reports. These examples illustrate how different industries can use Data Cloud reports to identify which customers or areas of business to focus on.

When you use Data Cloud reports and dashboards, your data is stored and processed in Data Cloud. Using Data Cloud features for reports and dashboards has billing implications.

These limits and limitations apply to Data Cloud reports and dashboards.

Keep these considerations in mind when working with Data Cloud reports on calculated insights.

Einstein Report Formula Generation can help you with the technical work of creating row-level and summary formulas. Describe a calculation in simple terms, and Einstein generative AI discovers the relevant data and suggests a formula.
title: Creating Custom Reports with Data Cloud
